item.title: JDK? DLed and not working?
item.dc:creator: @zstars zstars
item.description:
@zstars wrote:

Don’t use a batch script to compile. At least, first make sure that your Java is properly installed. Open a command line tool, type javac, and hit enter. If you get a “Javac is not a recognized command” error, or similar, then your environment variables are not set up correctly. If you need more help on setting up the JDK, you might wanna have a look at Tutorial 0 in my sig’s.
